'''諾蘭·詹姆斯·阿里納多'''（{{lang-en|'''Nolan James Arenado'''}}，{{bd|1991年|4月16日||}}），綽號「山大王」，為[[美國職棒|美國職棒]]大聯盟的三壘手，現效力於[[聖路易紅雀|聖路易紅雀]]。阿里納多從2013年進入大聯盟以來，其攻擊與防守兩端皆繳出統治大聯盟三壘防區的表現，因而被廣泛認為現役攻守最為全面的三壘手。阿里納多生涯獲得眾多榮譽，包含從新人年起金手套獎九連霸與白金手套獎五連霸。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
諾蘭·詹姆斯·阿里納多出生於[[加州|加州]][[新港滩|新港滩]]，而後在[[森林湖_(加利福尼亚州)|森林湖]]成長。自小便是[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]球迷<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2016/03/16/rockies-qa-everything-you-wanted-to-know-about-nolan-arenado/ |title=Rockies Q&A: Everything you wanted to know about Nolan Arenado – The Denver Post |accessdate=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2019-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702021722/https://www.denverpost.com/2016/03/16/rockies-qa-everything-you-wanted-to-know-about-nolan-arenado/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，高中起便擔任校隊游擊手<ref name=latimes>{{cite news |first=Eric |last=Sondheimer |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/apr/17/sports/sp-sondheimer17 |title=Mater Dei shortstops are long on talent |work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2009-04-17 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2015-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216012300/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/apr/17/sports/sp-sondheimer17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當時他的隊友還包括了[[奧斯汀·羅邁|奧斯汀·羅邁]]以及[[麥特·查普曼|麥特·查普曼]]等人<ref>{{cite news |last=Berg |first=Ted |url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2013/04/six-guys-set-to-become-mlb-stars/ |title=Six guys set to become MLB stars |work=[[今日美國|USA Today]] |date=2013-04-22 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130426002113/http://ftw.usatoday.com/2013/04/six-guys-set-to-become-mlb-stars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年，阿里納多率領校隊贏得了{{tsl|en|California Interscholastic Federation|加州校際聯盟}}的區域冠軍<ref>{{cite web |last=Fryer |first=Steve |url=http://www.ocvarsity.com/sports/toro-8997-chargers-three.html |title=Young El Toro doesn't wait, grabs Division II title |publisher=OC Varsity |date=2008-05-29 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140523225632/http://www.ocvarsity.com/sports/toro-8997-chargers-three.html |archivedate=2014-05-23 }}</ref>，當時他的成績是.456打擊率，32分打點，33得分，因此被[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]提名為「全明星隊」的一員{{efn|翌年，他的高中賽季成績再進一步，達到了懾人的.517打擊率，以及.615上壘率<ref name=impact>{{cite web |last=Pleskoff |first=Bernie |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130401&content_id=43651866&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |title=Rockies' prospect Arenado has impact bat |work=MLB.com |date=2013-04-01 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404072552/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130401&content_id=43651866&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並再次入選洛杉磯時報「全明星隊」<ref>{{cite newspaper |date=2009-06-18 |last=Bolch |first=Ben |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jun/18/sports/sp-baseball-all-stars18 |title=The Times' All-Star team |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2013-05-01 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218130848/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jun/18/sports/sp-baseball-all-stars18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/11/sports/sp-hsbaseball11 |work=Los Angeles Times |first=Dan |last=Arritt |title=The Times' high school all-star teams |date=2008-06-11 |accessdate=2015-02-09 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218130846/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/11/sports/sp-hsbaseball11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而後，[[亞利桑那州立大學|亞利桑那州立大學]]向阿里納多提供了全額獎學金<ref name=latimes/>。

=== 職業生涯 ===
==== 小聯盟時期 ====
阿里納多在2009年選秀會的第二輪被[[科羅拉多洛磯|科羅拉多洛磯]]選中，他選擇放棄亞大的獎學金，與洛磯簽約。2010年，阿里納多已經升上小聯盟1A球隊{{tsl|en|Asheville Tourists|阿什維爾旅人}}，當年他的賽季通算成績是.308打擊率，附帶41支二壘打<ref name=impact/>。2011年賽季開始之前，《{{tsl|en|Baseball America|棒球美國}}》將阿里納多評為洛磯系統的新秀第三佳（小聯盟第80位）<ref>{{cite web |last=Ringolsby |first=Tracy |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2011/2611160.html |title=Colorado Rockies Baseball America Top 10 prospects |work=Baseball America |date=2011-01-19 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2012-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009161621/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2011/2611160.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Report |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/top-100-prospects/2011/2611328.html |title=2011 Top 100 Prospects |work=Baseball America |date=2011-02-23 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2011-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226135537/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/top-100-prospects/2011/2611328.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過，在升上高階1A之前，阿里納多始終是打優於守的球員，當時他雖然有出色的臂力與柔軟度，在球場上的移動卻仍有待磨練，教練{{tsl|en|Jerry Weinstein|傑瑞·溫斯坦}}曾為此對他特別加力訓練。

2011年賽季，阿里納多在前半球季便累積了.283打擊率，6支全壘打，42分打點的成績，因此入選[[美國大聯盟未來之星明星賽|未來之星賽事]]{{efn|和阿里納多一同入選的，還有隊友[[威林·罗萨里奥|威林·罗萨里奥]]。附帶一提，在整個2011年賽季中，阿里納多最終打進了122分打點，領先整個小聯盟系統<ref name=asfg2012>{{cite news |last=Harding |first=Thomas |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120621&content_id=33692026&vkey=news_col&c_id=col |title=Arenado, Cabrera to play in All-Star Futures Game |work=MLB.com |date=2012-06-21 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130201052617/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120621&content_id=33692026&vkey=news_col&c_id=col |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}<ref name=asfg2011>{{cite news |last=Kosmider |first=Nick |url=http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110623&content_id=20913946&vkey=news_col&c_id=col |title=Rox land Rosario, Arenado in Futures Game |work=colorado.rockies.mlb.com |date=2011-06-23 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2014-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512225034/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110623&content_id=20913946&vkey=news_col&c_id=col |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，他亦是當年{{tsl|en|Arizona Fall League|亞利桑那秋季聯盟|亞利桑那秋聯}}的最有價值球員<ref name=aflmvp>{{cite web |last=Mayo |first=Jonathan |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20111119&content_id=26010606&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |title=Arenado named Arizona Fall League MVP |work=MLB.com |date=2011-11-20 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130206112933/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20111119&content_id=26010606&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite newspaper |last=Whicker |first=Mark |title=Arenado ‘automatic' in Arizona Fall League |url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/arenado-328316-league-wasn.html |work=Orange County Register |accessdate=2014-05-09 |date=2011-11-22 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924055009/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/arenado-328316-league-wasn.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年賽季，阿里納多二次入選未來之星賽事。

==== 科羅拉多洛磯 ====
;2013年賽季
縱使阿里納多在春訓的狀態良好，球團仍然決定安排他自小聯盟3A球隊展開新球季<ref>{{cite news |last=Renck |first=Troy |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_23123152/colorado-rockies-balancing-patience-urgency-nolan-arenado-case |title=Colorado Rockies balancing patience, urgency in Nolan Arenado case |work=[[丹佛邮报|The Denver Post]] |date=2010-09-14 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501050838/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_23123152/colorado-rockies-balancing-patience-urgency-nolan-arenado-case |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在4月結束前，阿里納多已經繳出.364打擊率，1.059攻擊指數的駭人成績，「迫使」洛磯球團將他正式升上大聯盟。4月28日，阿里納多在客場對陣[[亞利桑那響尾蛇|亞利桑那響尾蛇]]，然而他的大聯盟初登場並沒有擊出安打。翌日，他從[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]投手{{tsl|en|Josh Wall|喬什·沃爾}}手中擊出了一壘安打，是為他的大聯盟初安{{efn|當天洛磯以12-2大勝，阿里納多亦擊出了大聯盟生涯的第一支全壘打。}}<ref>{{cite newspaper |last=Plunkett |first=Bill |url=https://www.ocregister.com/2013/04/30/rockies-arenado-el-toro-high-has-a-night-of-firsts/ |title=Rockies’ Arenado (El Toro High) has a night of firsts |work=Orange County Register |date=2013-04-30 |accessdate=2018-04-18 |archive-date=2018-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180419053211/https://www.ocregister.com/2013/04/30/rockies-arenado-el-toro-high-has-a-night-of-firsts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月4日，在主場面對[[坦帕灣光芒|坦帕灣光芒]]的比賽中，面對強力投手[[大衛·普萊斯|大衛·普萊斯]]擊出了滿貫全壘打<ref>{{cite news |last=Buettner |first=Matthew |url=http://denver.cbslocal.com/2013/05/06/rockies-nolan-arenado-already-a-fan-favorite-after-8-days-in-the-majors/ |title=Rockies’ Nolan Arenado already a fan favorite after 8 days in the majors |work=KCNC-TV |date=2013-05-06 |accessdate=2018-04-18 |archive-date=2018-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180418230030/http://denver.cbslocal.com/2013/05/06/rockies-nolan-arenado-already-a-fan-favorite-after-8-days-in-the-majors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。防守端，阿里納多的評價甚至更佳，在[[DRS_(棒球)|DRS]]方面僅落後[[亞特蘭大勇士|亞特蘭大勇士]]的[[安德瑞爾頓·西蒙斯|安德瑞爾頓·西蒙斯]]{{efn|據定義，DRS（Defensive Runs Saved）指一個球員藉由防守比該位置的平均球員多守下或多丟多少分。2013年的阿里納多在該項數據的得分是30分，安德瑞爾頓·西蒙斯則是38分<ref>{{cite news |last=Simon |first=Mark |url=http://www.espn.com/blog/statsinfo/post/_/id/72007/nl-defensive-mvp-simmonsarenado-lead |title=NL Defensive MVP? Simmons/Arenado lead |work=ESPN.com |date=2013-09-07 |accessdate=2018-04-18 |archive-date=2018-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180419120713/http://www.espn.com/blog/statsinfo/post/_/id/72007/nl-defensive-mvp-simmonsarenado-lead |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。10月29日，防守金手套獎的名單公布，阿里納多以新人三壘手之姿奪獎，是國家聯盟史上首次<ref name=gg2013>{{cite newspaper |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |title=Rockies' Carlos Gonzalez, rookie Nolan Arenado win NL Gold Gloves |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_24414010/rockies-left-fielder-carlos-gonzalez-wins-third-gold |work=The Denver Post |accessdate=2014-05-09 |date=2013-10-29 |archive-date=2014-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512232409/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_24414010/rockies-left-fielder-carlos-gonzalez-wins-third-gold |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;2014年賽季
4月5日，阿里納多面對[[布蘭登·麥卡錫|布蘭登·麥卡錫]]兩次擊出全壘打，生涯首次單場多轟<ref>{{cite web |agency=Associated Press |url=http://denver.cbslocal.com/2014/04/05/arenado-rockies-rally-past-d-backs-9-4/ |title=Arenado, Rockies Rally Past D-Backs 9–4 |publisher=KCNC-TV CBS Denver |date=2014-04-05 |accessdate=2016-02-01 |archive-date=2016-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229135702/http://denver.cbslocal.com/2014/04/05/arenado-rockies-rally-past-d-backs-9-4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至5月8日止，他已連續28場比賽擊出安打，打破了洛磯隊史紀錄{{efn|原紀錄由[[麥克·卡戴爾|麥克·卡戴爾]]持有（27場，2013年）。}}<ref name=rockieshitstreak>{{cite web |title=Nolan Arenado sets Rockies record |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/10904785/nolan-arenado-hit-streak-reaches-28-breaks-colorado-rockies-record |publisher=ESPN.com |accessdate=2014-05-09 |date=2014-05-09 |archive-date=2014-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140509043836/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/10904785/nolan-arenado-hit-streak-reaches-28-breaks-colorado-rockies-record |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月23日，由於左手中指骨折，阿里納多首次進入傷兵名單<ref>{{cite news |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/rockies-third-baseman-nolan-arenado-breaks-finger-sliding-headfirst-into-second?ymd=20140523&content_id=76562074&vkey=news_mlb |title=Arenado breaks finger on headfirst slide, hits DL |last=Morgan |first=Joe |work=MLB.com |date=2014-05-24 |accessdate=2014-05-31 |archive-date=2014-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526205713/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/rockies-third-baseman-nolan-arenado-breaks-finger-sliding-headfirst-into-second?ymd=20140523&content_id=76562074&vkey=news_mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他錯過了37場常規賽，並於6月28日重新登錄。

阿里納多的狀態逐漸好轉，在8月的第三週，他有.545打擊率，1.645攻擊指數的表現，使他獲得國聯單週最佳球員的肯定<ref name=powaug2014>{{cite news |last=Schulman |first=Harry |url=http://blog.sfgate.com/giants/2014/08/25/sf-giants-need-to-pile-up-wins-against-rockies/ |title=SF Giants update: Tim Lincecum to miss next start |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle |date=2014-08-25 |accessdate=2016-02-10 |archive-date=2015-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921123311/http://blog.sfgate.com/giants/2014/08/25/sf-giants-need-to-pile-up-wins-against-rockies/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月份，由於胸骨挫傷引發了肺炎，阿里納多亦缺席了一些比賽。不過，即使僅出賽111場，他仍然獲得是年的防守金手套獎肯定。

;2015年賽季
6月第四週，阿里納多以7轟、14打點的成績再次獲選為國聯單週最佳球員<ref name=powjun2015>{{cite news |last=Groke |first=Nick |url=http://blogs.denverpost.com/rockies/2015/06/29/nolan-arenado-named-national-league-player-of-the-week-after-hot-streak/20302/ |title=Nolan Arenado named NL player of the week after hot streak, still trailing in all-star voting |newspaper=The Denver Post |date=2015-06-29 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410051720/http://blogs.denverpost.com/rockies/2015/06/29/nolan-arenado-named-national-league-player-of-the-week-after-hot-streak/20302/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他並入選了2015年的[[2015年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]。值得一提的是，在前半球季的24支全壘打（以及其他多項數據表現）當中，客場的數量比起主場要更佳<ref name=as2015>{{cite web |last=Bergstrom |first=Richard |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/sweetspot/post/_/id/60227/fans-should-get-to-know-new-all-star-nolan-arenado |title=Fans should get to know new All-Star Nolan Arenado |publisher=ESPN.com |date=2015-07-11 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216212440/http://espn.go.com/blog/sweetspot/post/_/id/60227/fans-should-get-to-know-new-all-star-nolan-arenado |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Groke |first=Nick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28442088/nolan-arenado-dj-lemahieu-named-mlb-all-star |title=Nolan Arenado, DJ LeMahieu named to NL all-star team; Troy Tulowitzki still pending |newspaper=The Denver Post |date=2015-07-06 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2015-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805192318/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28442088/nolan-arenado-dj-lemahieu-named-mlb-all-star |dead-url=no }}</ref>，打破了洛磯球員的「庫爾斯神話」{{efn|說明：洛磯主場所在的丹佛[[庫爾斯球場|庫爾斯球場]]由於海拔高度高，向來有利於打者發揮，投手在該球場則是處處受限。相對於此，洛磯球員離開主場的比賽表現（離開洛磯隊的轉隊球員亦然）經常成為話題，「下了山就不能打」的看法更是所在多有。}}。9月5日，阿里納多連續第六場比賽開轟，再次打破洛磯隊史紀錄{{efn|原紀錄由[[丹堤·比薛特|丹堤·比薛特]]以及Larry Walker共同持有（5場）。}}<ref name=hr6games>{{cite news |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28766787/nolan-arenado-gets-into-rockies-record-book-but |title=Nolan Arenado gets into Rockies' record book, but Giants win: Third Baseman sets franchise record with sixth consecutive home run game |newspaper=The Denver Post |date=2015-09-05 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216212155/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28766787/nolan-arenado-gets-into-rockies-record-book-but |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且以38支安打的表現獲得9月份國家聯盟最佳球員肯定。

2015年賽季，阿里納多在全壘打（42）、打點（130）、壘打數（354）、犧牲打（11）等多個項目領先於國家聯盟{{efn|阿里納多的國聯全壘打王頭銜（與[[布萊斯·哈波|布萊斯·哈波]]共享）是洛磯隊史自1997年後首見。領先全大聯盟的打點數同樣是隊史於1996年後首見。}}<ref name=2015nlhrleader>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/statistics/_/year/2015 |title=MLB Statistics - 2015 |website=ESPN |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2017-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114204041/http://www.espn.com/mlb/statistics/_/year/2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並首次獲得[[美國職棒大聯盟銀棒獎|銀棒獎]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=0&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=17,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2015 » Batters » Standard Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball |accessdate=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224024010/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=0&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=17,d |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ss2015>{{cite news |last=Groke |first=Nick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29109535/carlos-gonzalez-rockies-earns-silver-slugger-award |title=Rockies Nolan Arenado, Carlos Gonzalez win Silver Slugger awards |newspaper=The Denver Post |date=2015-11-12 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216212152/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29109535/carlos-gonzalez-rockies-earns-silver-slugger-award |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，他以89支長打打破了大聯盟三壘手的歷史紀錄{{efn|原紀錄由傳奇三壘手[[奇伯·瓊斯|奇伯·瓊斯]]持有（87，1999年）<ref name=pomsep2015/>。}}。

防守端，阿里納多連續第三年獲得三壘金手套，更在「{{tsl|en|Fielding Bible Award|防守聖經獎}}」等防守類獎項全面領先<ref>{{cite web |last=Miller |first=Doug |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/156972846/gold-glove-winners-announced |title=Defensive standouts nab Gold Glove Awards |website=MLB.com |date=2015-11-10 |accessdate=2015-11-10 |archive-date=2015-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112190850/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/156972846/gold-glove-winners-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=gg2015>{{cite web |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29099514/nolan-arenado-awarded-third-consecutive-national-league-gold |title=Rockies' Nolan Arenado awarded third consecutive NL Gold Glove |work=The Denver Post |date=2015-11-10 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160214212327/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29099514/nolan-arenado-awarded-third-consecutive-national-league-gold |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=fb2015>{{cite web |last=Harding |first=Thomas |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/156570936/nolan-arenado-wins-fielding-bible-award |title=Arenado wins Fielding Bible Award at third |website=MLB.com |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2015-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215194843/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/156570936/nolan-arenado-wins-fielding-bible-award |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=wilsondefpoy2015>{{cite web |last=Kubatko |first=Roch |url=http://www.masnsports.com/school-of-roch/2015/11/machado-denied-wilson-defensive-player-of-the-year-award.html |title=Machado denied Wilson Defensive Player of the Year Award |publisher=[[Mid-Atlantic_Sports_Network|MASN]].com |date=2015-11-11 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215234747/http://www.masnsports.com/school-of-roch/2015/11/machado-denied-wilson-defensive-player-of-the-year-award.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且首度獲得國家聯盟最有價值球員的記者投票。

;2016年賽季
[[File:Nolan_Arenado_on_August_31,_2016_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
在春訓開始前，阿里納多與洛磯球團達成了一年5,000,000美元的薪資協議，避免了仲裁<ref>{{cite news |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/news/rockies-avoid-arbitration-third-baseman-nolan-arenado-002804320--mlb.html |title=Rockies and third baseman Nolan Arenado reach $5M deal |work=Yahoo! Sports |date=2016-01-15 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2016-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222041202/http://sports.yahoo.com/news/rockies-avoid-arbitration-third-baseman-nolan-arenado-002804320--mlb.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這年他第二次入選[[2016年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]。8月8日，阿里納多在比賽中擊出全壘打，達成生涯100轟，25歲又4個月的年紀是洛磯隊史最年輕的紀錄<ref name=kosmider080816>{{cite news |last=Kosmider |first=Nick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2016/08/08/arenado-reaches-milestone-with-100th-home-run/ |title=Nolan Arenado reaches milestone with 100th home run: Arenado becomes youngest player in franchise history to reach mark |work=The Denver Post |date=2016-08-08 |accessdate=2016-08-13 |archive-date=2016-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810114906/http://www.denverpost.com/2016/08/08/arenado-reaches-milestone-with-100th-home-run/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。身體保持健康的阿里納多在2016年出賽了160場，他的佳績包括.294打擊率，182支安打（含82支長打），133分打點（大聯盟第一{{efn|含2015年在內，二度在打點項目領先整個大聯盟的表現，亦是洛磯隊史首次。}}）等數據，並且四次獲得金手套獎、銀棒獎、防守聖經獎等獎項的肯定。

;2017年賽季
這年，阿里納多再次選擇以協議的方式與洛磯球團磋商，最終的新合約數額以二年29,500,000美元議定<ref>{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.foxsports.com/mlb/story/rockies-arenado-agrees-to-29-5-million-2-year-contract-011317 |title=Rockies’ Arenado agrees to $29.5 million, 2-year contract |work=FoxSports.com |date=2017-01-13 |accessdate=2017-09-28 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929092513/http://www.foxsports.com/mlb/story/rockies-arenado-agrees-to-29-5-million-2-year-contract-011317 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月18日，在面對舊金山巨人的比賽中，阿里納多達成了[[完全打擊|完全打擊]]，包括結束比賽的[[再見全壘打|再見轟]]{{efn|這是大聯盟歷史上第288次完全打擊，洛磯隊史第8次。至於以再見全壘打完成完全打擊者，阿里納多則是第6次──前一人為洛磯球員[[卡洛斯·岡薩雷茲|卡洛斯·岡薩雷茲]]（2010年7月31日）。}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Snyder |first=Matt |title=Rockies' Nolan Arenado hits walk-off home run to complete the cycle vs. Giants |url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-nolan-arenado-hits-walk-off-home-run-to-complete-the-cycle-vs-giants/ |work=CBSSports.com |date=2017-06-18 |accessdate=2017-06-18 |archive-date=2017-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619104533/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-nolan-arenado-hits-walk-off-home-run-to-complete-the-cycle-vs-giants/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他再次入選[[2017年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]，並首次先發上場<ref name=saunders070217>{{cite newspaper |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/07/02/nolan-arenado-2017-colorado-rockies-all-stars/ |title=Nolan Arenado leads quartet of Rockies heading to MLB All-Star Game |work=Denver Post |date=2017-07-02 |accessdate=2017-07-19 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729100322/http://www.denverpost.com/2017/07/02/nolan-arenado-2017-colorado-rockies-all-stars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月19日與[[聖地牙哥教士|聖地牙哥教士]]的比賽中，阿里納多單場三次打出全壘打，收入7分打點，皆是個人新高<ref>{{cite news |last1=Cassavell |first1=A. J. |last2=Gelman |first2=Max |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/243178248/rockies-nolan-arenado-hits-3-hrs-vs-padres/?game_pk=491516 |title=Nolan, Nolan, Nolan: 3 HRs power Rox rout |work=MLB.com |date=2017-07-19 |accessdate=2017-07-19 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729094247/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/243178248/rockies-nolan-arenado-hits-3-hrs-vs-padres/?game_pk=491516 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且獲選為7月的國聯最佳球員<ref name=saunders080217>{{cite newspaper |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/08/02/nolan-arenado-national-league-july-player-of-the-month/ |title=Nolan Arenado, MVP candidate, named NL player of month for July |work=The Denver Post |date=2017-08-02 |accessdate=2017-08-07 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806114758/http://www.denverpost.com/2017/08/02/nolan-arenado-national-league-july-player-of-the-month/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這年他亦首次進入季後賽，在[[2017年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|國聯外卡賽]]中擊出全壘打，但球隊負於響尾蛇，無緣晉級<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI201710040.shtml |title=2017 National League Wild Card (NLWC), Rockies at Diamondbacks |work=Baseball-Reference.com |date=2017-10-04 |accessdate=2017-11-23 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201035447/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI201710040.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年季後，阿里納多的賽季打點數連續第三年達到130分（以上），是大聯盟歷史上第11次，三壘手位置則是首次有此成就<ref name=passan082417>{{cite news |last=Passan |first=Jeff |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/nolan-arenado-went-good-great-140632866.html |title=How Nolan Arenado went from good to great |work=Yahoo! Sports |date=2017-08-24 |accessdate=2017-09-17 |archive-date=2017-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917214203/https://sports.yahoo.com/nolan-arenado-went-good-great-140632866.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。個人獎項方面，阿里納多則是連續第五年獲得三壘金手套{{efn|以連續的金手套獎展開大聯盟生涯者，只有[[鈴木一朗|鈴木一朗]]的紀錄（連續10年）優於阿里納多<ref name=saunders110717>{{cite newspaper |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/11/07/nolan-arenado-dj-lemahieu-gold-glove-rockies/ |title=Rockies’ Nolan Arenado wins 5th Gold Glove; DJ LeMahieu snares his second |work=Denver Post |date=2017-11-07 |accessdate=2017-11-08 |archive-date=2017-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108071627/http://www.denverpost.com/2017/11/07/nolan-arenado-dj-lemahieu-gold-glove-rockies/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。

;2018年賽季
季前，《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》評選阿里納多為大聯盟總體能力第8位，尤其讚許他的防守能力<ref>{{cite magazine |author=SI.com Staff |url=https://www.si.com/mlb/2018/02/15/top-100-players-top-10-mike-trout-jose-altuve |title=SI's Top 100 MLB Players of 2018: The Top 10 |work=Sports Illustrated |date=2018-02-15 |accessdate=2018-02-17 |archive-date=2018-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180217223635/https://www.si.com/mlb/2018/02/15/top-100-players-top-10-mike-trout-jose-altuve |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在合約方面，阿里納多與洛磯球團協議在球季結束後就延長事宜商談，此舉有利他專注於場上的表現<ref>{{cite news |last=Varela |first=Ashley |url=http://mlb.nbcsports.com/2018/03/04/nolan-arenado-rockies-unlikely-to-reach-extension-this-spring/ |title=Nolan Arenado, Rockies unlikely to reach extension this spring |work=[[NBC_Sports|NBC Sports]] |date=2018-03-04 |accessdate=2018-03-04 |archive-date=2018-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305063654/http://mlb.nbcsports.com/2018/03/04/nolan-arenado-rockies-unlikely-to-reach-extension-this-spring/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他第二度在[[2018年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]中擔任國聯先發三壘手，球迷得票數則是第4位<ref name=harding071618>{{cite news |last=Harding |first=Thomas |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/nolan-arenado-leads-hot-rockies-into-break/c-286116180 |title=Arenado, Blackmon, Story lead resurgent Rox: All-Stars responsible for club's surge in NL West standings |work=MLB.com |date=2018-07-16 |accessdate=2018-07-18 |archive-date=2018-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717162958/https://www.mlb.com/news/nolan-arenado-leads-hot-rockies-into-break/c-286116180 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季後，他獲得個人第六座金手套獎，在國聯最有價值球員的票選中則排名第3位。

;2019年賽季
2019年2月26日，洛磯球團與阿里納多達成了八年260,000,000美元的合約協議<ref>{{cite news |last=Nightengale |first=Bob |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2019/02/26/nolan-arenado-rockies-offer-record-extension-contract/2989636002/ |title=Nolan Arenado agrees to eight-year, $260 million contract to stay with Rockies |work=USA Today |date=2019-02-26 |accessdate=2019-02-26 |archive-date=2019-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226182009/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2019/02/26/nolan-arenado-rockies-offer-record-extension-contract/2989636002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月25日，他在對陣[[巴爾的摩金鶯|巴爾的摩金鶯]]的比賽中擊出了個人生涯第200轟<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/nolan-arenado-hits-200th-career-home-run|title=Arenado launches 200th career homer|website=MLB.com|date=2019-05-26|accessdate=2020-02-16|archive-date=2020-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216184227/https://www.mlb.com/news/nolan-arenado-hits-200th-career-home-run|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在該年的[[2019年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]中，他再次獲票選擔任先發三壘手<ref name=etkin062819>{{cite magazine |last=Etkin |first=Jack |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jacketkin/2019/06/28/nolan-arenado-savors-latest-all-star-selection/#2eeba3c65286 |title=Nolan Arenado savors latest All-Star selection |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=2019-06-28 |accessdate=2019-06-30 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630065645/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jacketkin/2019/06/28/nolan-arenado-savors-latest-all-star-selection/#2eeba3c65286 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

